Class AlertInfoImpl

java.lang.Object
us.mn.state.dot.tms.server.BaseObjectImpl
us.mn.state.dot.tms.server.AlertInfoImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
SonarObject, AlertInfo, Storable
public class AlertInfoImpl extends BaseObjectImpl implements AlertInfo
CAP Alert Information is an object which is created when a CAP alert triggers one or more DMS to be deployed.
Author:
Michael Janson, Gordon Parikh, Douglas Lau
